    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take Notes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game presents you with a variety of logic puzzles that require both cleverness and analytical thinking. Each level offers unique challenges that will test your problem-solving skills, observance, and logical reasoning. With its diverse puzzles, this game provides not only great fun but also encourages creative and unconventional thinking. Every solution will bring satisfaction, making this game a perfect choice for all intellectual challenge enthusiasts. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features 40 diverse puzzles, each requiring a unique approach. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bunker</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate through the rooms of a mysterious research facility and uncover an untold story. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Something strange happened at the Fusion Energetics research facility. All personnel have disappeared without a trace, and the experimental reactor they were working on has become dangerously unstable. Your mission is to reach the control panel and shut it down before a disaster occurs. As if the situation weren't challenging enough, you'll have to bypass the facility’s puzzling security systems alone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094150/extras/a44eba5fbeac6412e279d6df644062de.avif?t=1762359639\" width=640 height=360 /></span></p>",
